summary: An ordinance accepting a deed dated the 19th day of January, 1920, from Carrie Fladland Kasen (formerly Carrie Fladland, a widow), and J. A. Kasen, her husband, of Seattle, Washington, to the City of Seattle, for lot 12, and the west half of lot 13, block 34, Denny & Hoyt's Addition to the City of Seattle, situated in King County, State of Washington.
